{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@property","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" (","kind":"text"},{"text":"nonatomic","kind":"keyword"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"When the value of this property is "},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and the map is tilted, the annotation"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"view appears smaller if it is towards the top of the view (closer to the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"horizon) and larger if it is towards the bottom of the view (closer to the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"viewpoint). This is also the behavior of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" objects. When the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"value of this property is "},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or the map’s pitch is zero, the annotation view"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"remains the same size regardless of its position on-screen."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The default value of this property is ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":". Keep this property set to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the view’s legibility is important."}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Scaling many on-screen annotation views can contribute to poor map","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"performance. Consider keeping this property disabled if your use case"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"involves hundreds or thousands of annotation views."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note","name":"Note","type":"aside"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"symbolKind":"property","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"scalesWithViewingDistance"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)scalesWithViewingDistance","roleHeading":"Instance Property","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L180","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"}},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","type":"topic","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}],"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage"},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"code":"UIImage","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"by the map view."}],"type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotationImage","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/scalesWithViewingDistance":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value that determines whether the annotation view grows and shrinks"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"as the distance between the viewpoint and the annotation view changes on a","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"tilted map.","type":"text"}],"title":"scalesWithViewingDistance","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/scalesWithViewingDistance","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/scaleswithviewingdistance","fragments":[{"text":"scalesWithViewingDistance","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotationView"}}}